videos.headline: Lindsay breaks free for Colorado's first TD of season
videos.description: Phillip Lindsay splits the defense for a huge 45-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: Nutt rips ball away from receiver for INT
videos.description: Kevin Nutt Jr. picks off Colorado's pass by stealing the ball straight out of the receiver's hands.

videos.headline: Johnson's leaping catch keeps Colorado State drive alive
videos.description: Nick Stevens threads the needle on third down to find Olabisi Johnson between three defenders.

videos.headline: Rams' Clark bursts out of the backfield for big gain
videos.description: Detrich Clark's 31-yard end-around provides a spark for Colorado State.

videos.headline: Nutt picks off pass in end zone for second INT of game
videos.description: Kevin Nutt Jr. jumps the Colorado receiver's route to record his second interception of the contest.

videos.headline: Colorado recovers fumble after long Rams completion
videos.description: Warren Jackson hauls in a 38-yard pass, but proceeds to cough up the ball for a turnover.
